Package: systemsettings
Section: kde
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: KDE System Settings Center
 KDE System Settings Center is the replacement for kcontrol. It is an improved
 user interface hosting various modules for configuring the desktop and other
 aspects of the system.
 .
 This package is part of KDE, and a component of the KDE base module.
 See the 'kde' and 'kdebase-workspace' packages for more information.

Package: kdebase-workspace-dbg
Section: devel
Architecture: any
Priority: extra
Depends: kdebase-workspace (= ${binary:Version}), kdepimlibs-dbg
Description: debugging symbols for kdebase-workspace
 This package contains the debugging symbols associated with kdebase-workspace.
 They will automatically be used by gdb for debugging kdebase-workspace-related
 issues.
